Welcome to PGSD!

ZFS Boot Environments:
  • Use 'beadm list' to view available boot environments
  • Create snapshots before system updates
  • Roll back with 'beadm activate <name>' if needed

System Information:
  • Arcan Display Server: /usr/local/bin/arcan
  • Durden Window Manager: /usr/local/share/arcan/appl/durden
  • Configuration: ~/.arcan/durden/

Documentation:
  • PGSD Wiki: https://pgsd.org/wiki (placeholder)
  • Arcan: https://arcan-fe.com
  • FreeBSD Handbook: https://docs.freebsd.org

